<h2>Introduction</h2>
As stated on the <a href="http://developer.berlios.de/projects/gale/">project page</a>, the "Graphics Abstraction Layer & Engine" is a object oriented wrapper for OpenGL and its extensions. GALE is designed to be modern, lightweight and self-consistent, and is particularly targeted at Demo Scene effects, tech demos and GPGPU applications.

